Date Slicer 8

In this step we are going to look at how to build date slicer.

Steps for this report

1. Drag and drop slicer from visualization and make it in between slicer.

2. Drag and drop date from calendar table

3. Add a title text and

  •     Background color- Maroon,
  •     Alignment - middle,
  •    Text size -16pt,
  •     Font family - Calibri. 

4. Slicer header - off

5.  Boarder - on

  • Color - white 30% darker
